<bibRefCitation author="Botosaneanu, L" journalOrPublisher="Revue d'Hydrobiologie Tropicale" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" pagination="197 - 207" title="Ecological observations on the caddisflies (Insecta: Trichoptera) from Trinidad and Tobago (W. Indies)." volume="25" year="1992">Botosaneanu and Sakal 1992</bibRefCitation>
